  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "''#GOTAGOHOME''; tear gas; Despite the high-pressure water attacks, people enter the President's House",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Thousands of protestors have come to Colombo since this morning with tear gas; The President entered the palace by breaking high-pressure water attacks and roadblocks.",
        "Police tear gas several times; Although efforts were made to quell the protests by using high-pressure water cannons and forcing President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa to resign, thousands of people entered the Presidential Palace by breaking the barricades around the Presidential Palace.",
        "A hospital spokesman told the BBC Sinhala service that 33 people, including members of the security forces, have been injured and are being treated at the Colombo National Hospital."
      ],
